text: Hell River also known as Partisans () and The Last Guerilla is a 1974 Serbian World War II movie directed by Stole Jankovic and starring Rod Taylor, Adam West, Brioni Farrell, Peter Carsten, Bata Živojinović, Branko Pleša, Janez Vrhovec, Dragomir Felba. ==Other websites== * * Category:1974 movies Category:1974 war movies Category:1970s war movies Category:Serbian movies Category:Liechtenstein movies Category:American war movies Category:World War II movies Category:Guerrilla warfare movies Category:Movies directed by Stole Jankovic
title: Hell River
